This is very simple game written in pygtk.
Therefore You Will need pygtk and python, tested to work on pygtk-2.12.1-r2 and Python 2.5.2.

Goal of the game:
Your goal is to rotate pieces so they are all connected.

Controls:
Click on a tile to rotate it
use arrow keys to move tile cursor
use Space to rotate tile under tile cursor

Author: Petr Sykora
